     Notice is hereby given that the U.S. Environmental
Protection Agency (EPA) Region II, is in receipt of  the
Resource Conservation and Recovery Act (RCRA) Part B permit
renewal application dated September 1, 1994, and the hazardous
waste incinerator risk assessment report dated October 7,
1994, submitted by:

